DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bootrealtime.uve.weibo.com,REJECT-200
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,brandvideo.biz.weibo.com,REJECT-200
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ctobsnssdk.com,REJECT-DICT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gdt.qq.com,REJECT-DICT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gdtimg.cn,REJECT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gdtimg.com,REJECT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,log.snssdk.com,REJECT-DICT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mdt.qq.com,REJECT-DICT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mssdk.volces.com,REJECT-DICT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mssdk3-normal-hl.zijieapi.com,REJECT-DICT
